50|$|The Book <b>of</b> <b>Habakkuk</b> is {{the eighth}} {{book of the}} 12 minor prophets of the Hebrew Bible. It is {{attributed}} to the prophet Habakkuk, and was probably composed in the late 7th century BC.|$|R
